1.Epandrium and associated features lateral view. 2. Same, ventral view. 3. Surstylus, inner view. 4. Phallus, lateral view.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,152,251]" pageId="3" pageNumber="180">
