<collectingCountry box="[327,394,189,215]" name="Japan" pageId="3" pageNumber="180">Japan</collectingCountry>
. The major family utilised was 
<taxonomicName box="[747,893,189,215]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Amanitaceae" kingdom="Fungi" order="Agaricales" pageId="3" pageNumber="180" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="family">Amanitaceae</taxonomicName>
